{"tid":1040669,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超強颱風「山竹」永久除名","createTime":"2019-02-28T08:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T10:51:42.000Z","uid":147376,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b48084924ee80f90bdb771040be0923c29d9c2dd","tid":1040669,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T08:57:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/article/20190227/s00004/1551261739161/%E8%B6%85%E5%BC%B7%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E3%80%8C%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9%E3%80%8D%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E9%99%A4%E5%90%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20190227%2Fs00004%2F1551261739161%2F%25E8%25B6%2585%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%25A2%25B1%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25AB%25B9%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E4%25B9%2585%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%2590%258D&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Tdz9kuezr8BQg8uGmIe3q97E%3D&h=b76a0eaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20190227%2Fs00004%2F1551261739161%2F%25E8%25B6%2585%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%25A2%25B1%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25AB%25B9%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E4%25B9%2585%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%2590%258D&h=d865586a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/article/20190227/s00004/1551261739161/%E8%B6%85%E5%BC%B7%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E3%80%8C%E5%B1%B1%E7%AB%B9%E3%80%8D%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E9%99%A4%E5%90%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n去年來勢洶洶的超強颱風「山竹」，肆虐本港及廣東期間，造成多處建築損毀及樹木倒塌，破壞嚴重。中國氣象局今日（27日）公布，在廣州舉行的第51屆世界氣象組織颱風委員會會議上，颱風「山竹（Mangkhut）」及「溫比亞（Rumbia）」被正式除名。<br />\n<br />\n世界颱風委員會年度會議常設的其中一個議題，是刪除過去一年造成嚴重影響颱風的名字，並要求相關成員重新命名。<span style=\"color: red;\">菲律賓在今屆會議上要求，除名2018年第22號颱風「山竹」，中國則提出除名2018年第18號颱風「溫比亞」</span>，相關新命名將由泰國和馬來西亞於下次會議提出。<br />\n<br />\n此外，會議通過了三個在2017年被除名的颱風新名字，包括由香港提供的「鴛鴦」會取替原本的「啟德」；<span style=\"color: red;\">日本提供的「野貓」取代「天鴿」；同樣由日本提供的「小狗」則會取替「天秤」。</span>有關譯名將由中國氣象局、香港天文台，聯同澳門地球物理暨氣象局商討後作準。<br />\n<br />\n由2000年1月1日起，世界氣象組織颱風委員會制訂了西北太平洋的熱帶氣旋新名單，由該委員會的14個國家或地區各自提供10個名字，共140個颱風名字。據了解，自2002年以來，西北太平洋和南海生成的颱風，已有45個被除名。"},{"pid":"325cab2e475fe5138aaa0ad6d1e84bfc2abbc656","tid":1040669,"uid":68607,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T08:58:47.000Z","msg":"「牛肉」正式入藉"},{"pid":"b466b822d75687a476327b2f2e1a75111bbeaf42","tid":1040669,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:14:00.000Z","msg":"已經好耐冇見重複啦"},{"pid":"9a21cd057ac5d86bbf87f44b4a4b269f40aa622b","tid":1040669,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:18:14.000Z","msg":"除左又點呢"},{"pid":"a378b58099350010b2387702f9795bc046ae19d4","tid":1040669,"uid":97708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:19:36.000Z","msg":"記得有個颱風叫風神 好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f022b3c46351aaac1d77fd5b226cb684bfde532","tid":1040669,"uid":65686,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a21cd057ac5d86bbf87f44b4a4b269f40aa622b","tid":1040669,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:18:14.000Z","msg":"除左又點呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:20:10.000Z","msg":"永久供奉"},{"pid":"f6ba7be67afff34842791a5b3942a34363b965df","tid":1040669,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4f022b3c46351aaac1d77fd5b226cb684bfde532","tid":1040669,"uid":65686,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a21cd057ac5d86bbf87f44b4a4b269f40aa622b","tid":1040669,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:18:14.000Z","msg":"除左又點呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:20:10.000Z","msg":"永久供奉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T09:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3652e6050212b6c6f0a53d9c2f125ad6a26b111a","tid":1040669,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28